[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     24[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - SSE-KMS encryption specified for S3
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     25[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - DynamoDB encryption at rest mentioned
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     26[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - TLS in transit specified ("all API calls over TLS")
