[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     28[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - CloudTrail enabled for all SageMaker and DynamoDB API calls
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     29[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - KMS for SageMaker training volumes and endpoints
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     30[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - De-identified data recommended for development
