[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    237[0m:[38;5;10m[49m | 2 | HIGH | Architecture | Architecture Diagram, Real-Time Inference | No error handling, circuit breaker, or DLQ for the inference path. Silent failures mean clinicians get no feedback; partial state failures could produce unsafe recommendations. | Add circuit breaker on SageMaker call, return explicit "no recommendation" on failure, CloudWatch alarms on error rates, prevent inference on stale/partial state. |
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    238[0m:[38;5;10m[49m | 3 | MEDIUM | Security | Code Step 6, store_recommendation() | Audit trail storage not specified as tamper-evident. Clinical decision logs for insulin dosing need immutability for regulatory and legal defensibility. | Add S3 Object Lock (compliance mode) as immutable archive alongside operational store. |
