[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    244[0m:[38;5;10m[49m | 9 | LOW | Security | Prerequisites, CloudTrail | DynamoDB data-plane operations not logged by CloudTrail by default. Every PHI access should be auditable. | Enable CloudTrail data events for patient-glucose-state table. |
